{
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "title": "Fraud Detection Dataset",
      "text": "%md\nDownloaded from here: https://www.kaggle.com/ealaxi/paysim1 \nAvailable here: gs://oklev-uku-datasets/fraud-detection\n\n\nPaySim simulates mobile money transactions based on a sample of real transactions extracted from one month of financial logs from a mobile money service implemented in an African country. The original logs were provided by a multinational company, who is the provider of the mobile financial service which is currently running in more than 14 countries all around the world.\n\nThis synthetic dataset is scaled down 1/4 of the original dataset and it is created just for Kaggle.\n",
      "user": "anonymous",
      "dateUpdated": "2026-03-17T00:47:07+0000",
      "progress": 0,
      "config": {
        "tableHide": false,
        "editorSetting": {
          "language": "markdown",
          "editOnDblClick": true,
          "completionSupport": false,
          "completionKey": "TAB"
        },
        "editorMode": "ace/mode/markdown",
        "colWidth": 12,
