      },
      "results": {
        "code": "SUCCESS",
        "msg": [
          {
            "type": "HTML",
            "data": "<div class=\"markdown-body\">\n<p>Downloaded from here: <a href=\"https://www.kaggle.com/ealaxi/paysim1\">https://www.kaggle.com/ealaxi/paysim1</a><br />\nAvailable here: <a href=\"gs://oklev-uku-datasets/fraud-detection\">gs://oklev-uku-datasets/fraud-detection</a></p>\n<p>PaySim simulates mobile money transactions based on a sample of real transactions extracted from one month of financial logs from a mobile money service implemented in an African country. The original logs were provided by a multinational company, who is the provider of the mobile financial service which is currently running in more than 14 countries all around the world.</p>\n<p>This synthetic dataset is scaled down 1/4 of the original dataset and it is created just for Kaggle.</p>\n\n</div>"
          }
        ]
      },
